{"iti55:0.1":"Itivuttaka 55 ","iti55:0.2":"Tikanipata ","iti55:0.3":"Pathamavagga ","iti55:0.4":"Dutiyaesanasutta ","iti55:1.1":"Vuttanhetam bhagavata vuttamarahatati me sutam: ","iti55:2.1":"“Tisso ima, bhikkhave, esana. ","iti55:2.2":"Katama tisso? ","iti55:2.3":"Kamesana, bhavesana, brahmacariyesana—","iti55:2.4":"ima kho, bhikkhave, tisso esana”ti. ","iti55:2.5":"Etamattham bhagava avoca. ","iti55:2.6":"Tatthetam iti vuccati: ","iti55:3.1":"“Kamesana bhavesana, ","iti55:3.2":"brahmacariyesana saha; ","iti55:3.3":"Iti saccaparamaso, ","iti55:3.4":"ditthitthana samussaya. ","iti55:4.1":"Sabbaragavirattassa, ","iti55:4.2":"tanhakkhayavimuttino; ","iti55:4.3":"Esana patinissattha, ","iti55:4.4":"ditthitthana samuhata; ","iti55:4.5":"Esananam khaya bhikkhu, ","iti55:4.6":"niraso akathankathi”ti. ","iti55:5.1":"Ayampi attho vutto bhagavata, iti me sutanti. ","iti55:5.2":"Chattham. "}